WORD = [{ reference: 'Gen 15:1', text: 'After these things the word of YHVH came to Abram in a vision: “Fear not, Abram, I am your shield; your reward shall be very great.”' }, { reference: 'Gen 15:4', text: 'And behold, the word of YHVH came to him: “This man shall not be your heir; your very own son shall be your heir.”' }, { reference: 'Gen 37:14', text: 'So he said to him, “Go now, see if it is well with your brothers and with the flock, and bring me word.” So he sent him from the Valley of Hebron, and he came to Shechem.' }, { reference: 'Gen 38:25', text: 'As she was being brought out, she sent word to her father-in-law, “By the man to whom these belong, I am pregnant.” And she said, “Please identify whose these are, the signet and the cord and the staff.”' }, { reference: 'Gen 44:18', text: "Then Judah went up to him and said, “Oh, my lord, please let your servant speak a word in my lord's ears, and let not your anger burn against your servant, for you are like Pharaoh himself." }, { reference: 'Exo 8:13', text: 'And YHVH did according to the word of Moses. The frogs died out in the houses, the courtyards, and the fields.' }, { reference: 'Exo 9:20', text: 'Then whoever feared the word of YHVH among the servants of Pharaoh hurried his slaves and his livestock into the houses,' }, { reference: 'Exo 9:21', text: 'but whoever did not pay attention to the word of YHVH left his slaves and his livestock in the field.' }, { reference: 'Exo 18:6', text: 'And when he sent word to Moses, “I, your father-in-law Jethro, am coming to you with your wife and her two sons with her,”' }, { reference: 'Exo 32:28', text: 'And the sons of Levi did according to the word of Moses. And that day about three thousand men of the people fell.' }, { reference: 'Exo 33:4', text: 'When the people heard this disastrous word, they mourned, and no one put on his ornaments.' }, { reference: 'Exo 36:6', text: 'So Moses gave command, and word was proclaimed throughout the camp, “Let no man or woman do anything more for the contribution for the sanctuary.” So the people were restrained from bringing,' }, { reference: 'Lev 10:7', text: 'And do not go outside the entrance of the tent of meeting, lest you die, for the anointing oil of YHVH is upon you.” And they did according to the word of Moses.' }, { reference: 'Num 3:16', text: 'So Moses listed them according to the word of YHVH, as he was commanded.' }, { reference: 'Num 3:51', text: 'And Moses gave the redemption money to Aaron and his sons, according to the word of YHVH, as YHVH commanded Moses.' }, { reference: 'Num 11:23', text: "And YHVH said to Moses, “Is YHVH's hand shortened? Now you shall see whether my word will come true for you or not.”" }, { reference: 'Num 13:26', text: 'And they came to Moses and Aaron and to all the congregation of the people of Israel in the wilderness of Paran, at Kadesh. They brought back word to them and to all the congregation, and showed them the fruit of the land.' }, { reference: 'Num 14:20', text: 'Then YHVH said, “I have pardoned, according to your word.' }, { reference: 'Num 15:31', text: 'Because he has despised the word of YHVH and has broken his commandment, that person shall be utterly cut off; his iniquity shall be on him.”' }, { reference: 'Num 22:8', text: 'And he said to them, “Lodge here tonight, and I will bring back word to you, as YHVH speaks to me.” So the princes of Moab stayed with Balaam.' }, { reference: 'Num 22:35', text: 'And the angel of YHVH said to Balaam, “Go with the men, but speak only the word that I tell you.” So Balaam went on with the princes of Balak.' }, { reference: 'Num 22:38', text: 'Balaam said to Balak, “Behold, I have come to you! Have I now any power of my own to speak anything? The word that God puts in my mouth, that must I speak.”' }, { reference: 'Num 23:5', text: "And YHVH put a word in Balaam's mouth and said, “Return to Balak, and thus you shall speak.”" }, { reference: 'Num 23:16', text: 'And YHVH met Balaam and put a word in his mouth and said, “Return to Balak, and thus shall you speak.”' }, { reference: 'Num 24:13', text: "‘If Balak should give me his house full of silver and gold, I would not be able to go beyond the word of YHVH, to do either good or bad of my own will. What YHVH speaks, that will I speak'?" }, { reference: 'Num 27:14', text: 'because you rebelled against my word in the wilderness of Zin when the congregation quarreled, failing to uphold me as holy at the waters before their eyes.” (These are the waters of Meribah of Kadesh in the wilderness of Zin.)' }, { reference: 'Num 27:21', text: 'And he shall stand before Eleazar the priest, who shall inquire for him by the judgment of the Urim before YHVH. At his word they shall go out, and at his word they shall come in, both he and all the people of Israel with him, the whole congregation.”' }, { reference: 'Num 30:2', text: 'If a man vows a vow to YHVH, or swears an oath to bind himself by a pledge, he shall not break his word. He shall do according to all that proceeds out of his mouth.' }, { reference: 'Num 36:5', text: 'And Moses commanded the people of Israel according to the word of YHVH, saying, “The tribe of the people of Joseph is right.' }, { reference: 'Deu 1:22', text: "Then all of you came near me and said, ‘Let us send men before us, that they may explore the land for us and bring us word again of the way by which we must go up and the cities into which we shall come.'" }, { reference: 'Deu 1:25', text: "And they took in their hands some of the fruit of the land and brought it down to us, and brought us word again and said, ‘It is a good land that YHVH our God is giving us.'" }, { reference: 'Deu 1:32', text: 'Yet in spite of this word you did not believe YHVH your God,' }, { reference: 'Deu 4:2', text: 'You shall not add to the word that I command you, nor take from it, that you may keep the commandments of YHVH your God that I command you.' }, { reference: 'Deu 5:5', text: 'while I stood between YHVH and you at that time, to declare to you the word of YHVH. For you were afraid because of the fire, and you did not go up into the mountain. He said:' }, { reference: 'Deu 8:3', text: 'And he humbled you and let you hunger and fed you with manna, which you did not know, nor did your fathers know, that he might make you know that man does not live by bread alone, but man lives by every word that comes from the mouth of YHVH.' }, { reference: 'Deu 9:5', text: 'Not because of your righteousness or the uprightness of your heart are you going in to possess their land, but because of the wickedness of these nations YHVH your God is driving them out from before you, and that he may confirm the word that YHVH swore to your fathers, to Abraham, to Isaac, and to Jacob.' }, { reference: 'Deu 18:20', text: "But the prophet who presumes to speak a word in my name that I have not commanded him to speak, or who speaks in the name of other gods, that same prophet shall die.'" }, { reference: 'Deu 18:21', text: "And if you say in your heart, ‘How may we know the word that YHVH has not spoken?'—" }, { reference: 'Deu 18:22', text: 'when a prophet speaks in the name of YHVH, if the word does not come to pass or come true, that is a word that YHVH has not spoken; the prophet has spoken it presumptuously. You need not be afraid of him.' }, { reference: 'Deu 21:5', text: 'Then the priests, the sons of Levi, shall come forward, for YHVH your God has chosen them to minister to him and to bless in the name of YHVH, and by their word every dispute and every assault shall be settled.' }, { reference: 'Deu 30:14', text: 'But the word is very near you. It is in your mouth and in your heart, so that you can do it.' }, { reference: 'Deu 32:47', text: 'For it is no empty word for you, but your very life, and by this word you shall live long in the land that you are going over the Jordan to possess.”' }, { reference: 'Deu 33:9', text: "who said of his father and mother, ‘I regard them not'; he disowned his brothers and ignored his children. For they observed your word and kept your covenant." }, { reference: 'Deu 34:5', text: 'So Moses the servant of YHVH died there in the land of Moab, according to the word of YHVH,' }, { reference: 'Jos 1:13', text: "“Remember the word that Moses the servant of YHVH commanded you, saying, ‘YHVH your God is providing you a place of rest and will give you this land.'" }, { reference: 'Jos 6:10', text: 'But Joshua commanded the people, “You shall not shout or make your voice heard, neither shall any word go out of your mouth, until the day I tell you to shout. Then you shall shout.”' }, { reference: 'Jos 8:8', text: 'And as soon as you have taken the city, you shall set the city on fire. You shall do according to the word of YHVH. See, I have commanded you.”' }, { reference: 'Jos 8:27', text: 'Only the livestock and the spoil of that city Israel took as their plunder, according to the word of YHVH that he commanded Joshua.' }, { reference: 'Jos 8:35', text: 'There was not a word of all that Moses commanded that Joshua did not read before all the assembly of Israel, and the women, and the little ones, and the sojourners who lived among them.' }, { reference: 'Jos 14:7', text: 'I was forty years old when Moses the servant of YHVH sent me from Kadesh-barnea to spy out the land, and I brought him word again as it was in my heart.' }].freeze
